  "lines": [
    {
      "text": "How's it going, everybody?",
      "start": 5634,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2436
    },
    {
      "text": "My name is Flash Goren.",
      "start": 5637,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2437
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm Bosnian.",
      "start": 5639,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2438
    },
    {
      "text": "And I don't know what that means either.",
      "start": 5640,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2439
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah, I don't even know my own stereotypes,",
      "start": 5644,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2440
    },
    {
      "text": "which is kind of weird.",
      "start": 5647,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2441
    },
    {
      "text": "All I know is that other Europeans get very nervous",
      "start": 5649,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2442
    },
    {
      "text": "when I'm around them.",
      "start": 5653,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2443
    },
    {
      "text": "And-- and you're welcome.",
      "start": 5656,
      "label": "tag",
      "line_number": 2444
    },
    {
      "text": "That's all I have to say about that.",
      "start": 5663,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2445
    },
    {
      "text": "If somebody came up to me and said,",
      "start": 5666,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2446
    },
    {
      "text": "all Bosnians are bad drivers, my response",
      "start": 5668,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2447
    },
    {
      "text": "would be, what else?",
      "start": 5670,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2448
    },
    {
      "text": "I want to know.",
      "start": 5676,
      "label": "tag",
      "line_number": 2449
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm going to get my Glock out and take some notes.",
      "start": 5679,
      "label": "tag",
      "line_number": 2450
    },
    {
      "text": "Glock also makes pens.",
      "start": 5683,
      "label": "tag",
      "line_number": 2451
    },
    {
      "text": "Not everyone knows that.",
      "start": 5684,
      "label": "tag",
      "line_number": 2452
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm not the best representative from Bosnians.",
      "start": 5687,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2453
    },
    {
      "text": "I know that I forgot most of the language.",
      "start": 5691,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2454
    },
    {
      "text": "And I'm a good driver.",
      "start": 5694,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2455
    },
    {
      "text": "And also--",
      "start": 5696,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2456
    },
    {
      "text": "[HORN HONKING]",
      "start": 5698,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2457
    },
    {
      "text": "I think I just forgot the rest.",
      "start": 5701,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2458
    },
    {
      "text": "Thanks, guys.",
      "start": 5702,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2459
    }
  ]
}